title: Wrong data set result returned when an invalid filter expression is set for row[0]
description: Then when setting a filter like 'row[0] equals to 0', the result set is either null or incorrect.
OB: When setting a filter in the dataset with the expression 'row[0] equals to'
EB: The first result record is returned when previewing.
SR:
1. Set a filter in the dataset using the expression 'row[0] equals to'
2. Click on the Preview tab
